Privacy Policy
Dmytro Denys built the Hexogonal Mosaic app as a Commercial app.
We do not collect or store user's personal information. We don't require you to provide any information.
We have access to the information about users of the app, only in aggregate and anonymized form (e.g., number of downloads for Country, number of purchases, crashes, ...). We are not able to connect this information to a specific person or device.
We provide support by email. The information you send us when you ask for support, are used only for this purpose. We do not sell or give this information to other entities.
Changes to This Privacy Policy
I may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. Thus, you are advised to review this page periodically for any changes. I will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page. These changes are effective immediately after they are posted on this page.
These terms and conditions are effective as of 2021-05-21
Contact Us
If you have any questions or suggestions about my Privacy Policy, do not hesitate to contact me at http://sevenfoots.com/contacts.